comments: Nancy and Gayle are the best ever!
I loved her class. She is nurturing to her students and has obvious passion for what she is teaching. She has been, by far, my favorite nursing instructor.

I enjoyed this instructor and thought that she was very detailed. She took the time to meet with you and go over any information that was not clear. I retained more in this class than I have in any of my other classes.

Very Much Enjoy Nancy\'s class. She\'s straight forward, and informative. Not sure why someone would say "reads from the book" - if so, she changed! she gives great lectures - and yes, you do need to watch the online lectures! I\'d take her every semester if I could!

Nancy is a good instructor and it is obvious that OB is her world. I\'m in the bridge program. Her tests aren\'t bad, but you must watch the streaming videos to pass. She is willing to meet with you and help you if needed. Just watch the videos, work on your care plans and you will be fine!
